### ===========================
### Admin Category Management
### ===========================

### List root categories
# Fetches root-level categories with admin-specific fields.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories?depth=1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### List root categories with depth 2
# Fetches root categories and their immediate children.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories?depth=2
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get category details
# Fetches detailed information about a single category.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get category children
# Fetches the subcategories of a given category with admin-specific fields.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1/children?depth=1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Search categories
# Searches categories by name, including hidden categories.
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories/search?q=electr&limit=10
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### ===========================
### Create Category
### ===========================

### Create a root category
# Creates a new GIMLEE category at the root level.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": {
    "en-US": "Custom Category",
    "pl-PL": "Kategoria Niestandardowa"
  }
}

### Create a child category
# Creates a new GIMLEE category under an existing parent.
POST {{host}}/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": {
    "en-US": "Subcategory",
    "pl-PL": "Podkategoria"
  },
  "parentId": 1
}

### ===========================
### Update Category
### ===========================

### Update category name
# Updates names for multiple languages.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "name": {
    "en-US": "Updated Category Name",
    "pl-PL": "Zaktualizowana Nazwa Kategorii"
  }
}

### Update category slug
# Overrides auto-generated slugs with custom ones.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "slug": {
    "en-US": "custom-slug",
    "pl-PL": "niestandardowy-slug"
  }
}

### ===========================
### Hide / Show Category
### ===========================

### Hide category (check for active ads)
# First call without acknowledge - returns affected ad count if any.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "hidden": true
}

### Hide category (confirmed)
# With acknowledge=true, hides category and deactivates active ads.
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "hidden": true,
  "acknowledge": true
}

### Show category
# Un-hides a single category (does not cascade to children).
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "hidden": false
}

### ===========================
### Reorder Category
### ===========================

### Move category up among siblings
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "direction": "UP"
}

### Move category down among siblings
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "direction": "DOWN"
}

### ===========================
### Move Category
### ===========================

### Move category to a new parent
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/5/move
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "newParentId": 10
}

### Move category to root level
PATCH {{host}}/api/admin/categories/5/move
Content-Type: application/json
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "newParentId": null
}

### ===========================
### Delete Category
### ===========================

### Delete a GML category
# Only GIMLEE categories with no children and no ads can be deleted.
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/categories/100
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### ===========================
### Error Scenarios
### ===========================

### Attempt to delete a GPT category (expect 400)
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Attempt to delete category with children (expect 409)
DELETE {{host}}/api/admin/categories/1
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Attempt to access without ADMIN role (expect 403)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/categories
Accept-Language: en-US
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
